name: PS5 Website Template
description:
A pandemic, stuck inside, PS5 stock issues. When the PS5 was first released there was massive stock issues which made it really hard for your everyday person to buy one.


I created the PS5 Stock 101 website with the aim to help make it easier for all the gamers in the UK to find out when to grab a PS5 next.


Grab this PS5 website template and have fun grabbing the assets and the little emoticons i made.


Live Website: ps5stock101.co.uk

Contact me: https://twitter.com/furquan101
